parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbags can cause metal debris to spray occupants, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning indicator illuminated
inability to repair or replace airbags due to parts unavailability
concern for safety while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heating element in the driver's seat can cause discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: Heating element in the driver's seat does not work
heating element turns off quickly
heating element only turns on for a brief minute.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal travels to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the ABS warning light is illuminated
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
and the vehicle experiences intermittent brake failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall repairs can leave vehicles with safety defects on the road, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle has a recall notice
but the parts are not available for repair
and the dealer or manufacturer is unable to provide a timeline for when the parts will be available.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in providing recall repairs can leave vehicles with safety defects on the road, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle has a recall notice
but the repairs are delayed

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective chrome wheel rims can cause air leaks, leading to tire pressure loss, which can result in accidents, tire blowouts, or leave the driver stranded. This issue can also lead to frequent tire replacements, causing inconvenience and financial loss to the vehicle owner.
symptoms: Air leaks from tires
frequent tire pressure loss
chrome flaking or peeling off the wheels
hairline cracks in the wheels
wheels not holding tire pressure
tires coming off the rim while driving
and constant need to add air to the tires.
